WEBVTT

1
00:54:59.690 --> 00:55:00.680 
别忘了我们
Don't forget about us.

2
00:55:00.680 --> 00:55:02.480 
不会的 乔 我只离开一个星期
I won't Jo, it's only a week.

3
00:55:02.480 --> 00:55:04.500 
-这太漂亮了 -它不是你的
- It's beautiful. - It's not yours.

4
00:55:04.640 --> 00:55:05.970 
我戴着会很好看
It would look very good on me.

5
00:55:05.970 --> 00:55:08.120 
她需要双像样的鞋
She needs to have some decent shoes.

6
00:55:08.120 --> 00:55:12.490 
谢谢你的马车 劳伦斯先生 我都不知道该怎么感谢您
Thank you for the carriage, Mr. Laurence. I don't know how to repay you.

7
00:55:12.620 --> 00:55:14.580 
别这么见外
Nonsense. Nonsense.

8
00:55:15.800 --> 00:55:17.610 
还有一件事
Although there is one thing.

9
00:55:17.610 --> 00:55:22.230 
今天我突然想起来我女儿的钢琴很少使用
It occurred to me today that my daughter's piano suffers from want of use.

10
00:55:22.230 --> 00:55:26.190 
你的这些女孩们想时不时过来练习钢琴吗
Any of your girls like to run over, and practice on it now and then,

11
00:55:26.190 --> 00:55:28.050 
这样就能保持它的音准了
just to keep it in tune?

12
00:55:28.050 --> 00:55:30.280 
如果她们不想来 那就算了
If they don't care to come, then never mind.

